def calculate_dot_winning_probability(yakko_points, wakko_points):
    max_points = max(yakko_points, wakko_points)
    favorable_outcomes = 7 + max_points
    total_outcomes = 6

    def gcd(a, b):
        while b:
            (a, b) = (b, a % b)
        return a
    gcd_value = gcd(favorable_outcomes, total_outcomes)
    numerator = favorable_outcomes // gcd_value
    denominator = total_outcomes // gcd_value
    return f'{numerator}/{denominator}'
